{"tid":799711,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗尼一家拍真人騷搵銀","createTime":"2018-08-30T09:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T09:53:29.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2b02310b0983e2484b6609d2f83ddb13b7d72fa8","tid":799711,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180830/photo/bkn-20180830170500482-0830_00882_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180830170500482-0830_00882_001_01p.jpg&h=37c734e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英格蘭球星朗尼登陸美職後，立即成為美國大紅人，佢老婆麥露蓮同4個囝囝亦深受注目，據報著名市場公司Octagon睇中朗尼一家嘅吸金力，準備同佢哋簽贊助合約，希望朗尼一家可以推廣體動產品、食物、電話同汽車等產品，甚至乎拍埋真人Show！如果成功合作，預計朗尼嘅收入可以超越碧咸當年喺美職賺嘅1.75億英鎊！<br />\n<br />\nOctagon喺美國體壇有一定影響力，NBA球星史提芬居里同泳壇名將菲比斯都係佢哋合作伙伴，消息人士透露：「朗尼一家人都好鍾意美國嘅生活，依家已經有唔少品牌排住隊嚟搵佢合作，甚至乎商討緊開拍真人Show嘅可能性。」"},{"pid":"c5220aaae420f328113adebf1b7c10f9abeda497","tid":799711,"uid":58811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"王騎出po見到個朗字以為係C朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f2f402eaff48bee4a8bd38742712b6d2467e7c","tid":799711,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"拍朗尼去叫老雞？"},{"pid":"e09e9c3368a3059681f91c7723ece0c73ddfeee5","tid":799711,"uid":201731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"黑人食屎會變咩 ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吏力架"}]}